---
// About section — dark gradient, intro text, portrait tile
---
<section id="omne" class="about">
  <div class="about-inner">
    <div class="about-text">
      <h2 class="section-title">
        Tvorím <em style="font-weight:300;color:var(--muted);">priestory</em>, hľadám mierku.
      </h2>
      <p>
        Som študentka architektúry. 
      </p>
      <p class="muted">
        Toto portfólio zahŕňa výber školských projektov z dvoch semestrov.
      </p>
      <dl class="about-facts">
        <dt>Štúdium</dt><dd>VŠB TUO  ·  2025 - dnes</dd>
        <dt>Lokalita</dt><dd>Ostrava · CZ</dd>
        <dt>Software</dt><dd>AutoCAD · Rhino · Adobe</dd>
      </dl>
    </div>
    <div class="about-portrait tile dark">
      <span class="pip">portrét — 01</span>
      <svg class="tile-arch" viewBox="0 0 400 500" preserveAspectRatio="none">
        <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="80" stroke-width="1.25" fill="none" />
        <path d="M80 460 Q200 320 320 460" stroke-width="1.25" fill="none" />
      </svg>
      <span class="tile-caption">portrét</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>